  "text": "[8] In the first section of this study, we used the MODIS fire data in the shape file format in order to use them in GIS (geographic information system) maps. These were obtained from the University of Maryland; more information on archived fire data is described by [CITATION_1] . In the transport study, the fire product MOD14 Collection 5 data have been utilized where fire pixels were combined with the smoke plume image from MISR.",
